{"_response_info":{"status":"ok"},"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/glaucoma-and-driving.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/glaucoma-and-driving","title":"Glaucoma and driving","format":"answer","updated_at":"2012-10-22T15:14:16+00:00","details":{"need_id":"2417","business_proposition":false,"description":"You may need to tell DVLA If you have glaucoma – if you do, download the correct form to let them know","language":"en","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>You may need to tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr> if you have glaucoma.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice help-notice\">\n<p>You can be fined up to £1,000 if you don’t tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr> about a medical condition that affects your driving. If you’re involved in an accident, you may be prosecuted.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Car or motorcycle licence</h2>\n\n<h3>If glaucoma only affects one eye</h3>\n\n<p>You don&rsquo;t need to tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr> provided you have no medical condition in the other eye and you&rsquo;re still able to meet the <a href=\"/driving-eyesight-rules\" title=\"Driving eyesight rules\">&lsquo;visual standards for driving&rsquo;</a>.</p>\n\n<p>For more information read the vision information leaflet &lsquo;VIS1&rsquo;.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@motor/documents/digitalasset/dg_065298.pdf\" title=\"Download leaflet 'VIS1: A guide to standards of vision for driving cars and motorcycles' (PDF, 209KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘VIS1 - A guide to standards of vision for driving cars and motorcycles’ (PDF, 209KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h3>If glaucoma affects both eyes</h3>\n\n<p>You must tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. Fill in form V1 and send it to <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. The address is on the form.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@motor/documents/digitalasset/dg_065620.pdf\" title=\"Download medical questionnaire\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘V1 - Confidential medical information’ (PDF, 253KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Bus, coach or lorry licence</h2>\n\n<p>You must tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. Fill in form V1V and send it to <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. The address is on the form.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@motor/documents/digitalasset/dg_065275.pdf\" title=\"Download medical questionnaire\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘V1V - Confidential medical information’ (PDF, 261KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n","alternative_title":""},"tags":[],"related":[{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/driving-if-disabled.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/driving-if-disabled","title":"Medical conditions, disabilities and driving","format":"guide","updated_at":"2012-11-14T12:25:08+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/health-conditions-and-driving.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/health-conditions-and-driving","title":"Health conditions and driving","format":"answer","updated_at":"2012-10-22T15:25:48+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/giving-up-your-driving-licence.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/giving-up-your-driving-licence","title":"Surrendering your driving licence","format":"answer","updated_at":"2012-11-14T12:45:33+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/reapply-driving-licence-medical-condition.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/reapply-driving-licence-medical-condition","title":"Re-apply for a driving licence following a medical condition","format":"answer","updated_at":"2012-11-30T12:27:11+00:00"}]}